cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.PF

Reasoning: 
1. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper focuses on efficient management of data centres, which is a key area of research in distributed and cluster computing. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the assignment of virtual machines on servers, which can be viewed as an optimization problem that can be solved using AI techniques. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the efficient management of a data centre, which involves controlling the energy consumption of servers. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the efficient management of data centres, which are an integral part of the internet infrastructure. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) - The paper focuses on minimizing energy costs while ensuring service quality, which is a key aspect of performance optimization in data centres.
